title: Eggs Trendedict 1/5: XXL, Tanya Roberts, Matt James, PAGOP, NBA
itunes:title: Eggs Trendedict 1/5: XXL, Tanya Roberts, Matt James, PAGOP, NBA
description:
On this edition of Eggs Trendedict Jack and Miles discuss XXL asking their audience about varying degrees of rapper quality, Tanya Roberts has passed (officially), the new season of the Bachelor has started featuring Matt James, Pennsylvania state Republicans are further blocking elected officials from taking seats in an attempt to try and overturn the general election, and the boys discuss their NBA Mount Rushmore.
